docs {
Updates an existing Okta managed user account specified by ID.

You can only update the `name`, `description`, `ownerUserIds`, and `ownerGroupIds` properties.

**Responses:**
- `200`: Success
- `400`: 
- `403`: 
- `404`: 
- `429`:
}
